g bowl lid and weigh 250 g of the stock into it. Add remaining stock to chicken and rice and cover to keep warm. Clean and dry mixing bowl."},{"content":"Place egg into mixing bowl and mix <b>30 sec\/speed 8<b>."},{"content":"Add lemon juice and mix <b>30 sec\/speed 5<b>."},{"content":"Further mix <b>20 sec\/speed 2<b>, slowly adding reserved stock through hole in mixing bowl lid until combined and frothy."},{"content":"Transfer lemon mixture into bowl with chicken, rice and stock and gently combine. Transfer into serving bowls, garnish with parsley and serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> or <i>Everyday Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 15m","4 portions"]}